{"tid":559710,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個國家或地區嘅人最鍾意講粗口？","createTime":"2018-02-13T11:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T12:05:40.000Z","uid":155084,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c821c7d5458da7303cfc15f896a4366db81ad35","tid":559710,"uid":155084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:55:57.000Z","msg":"唔洗諗，一定係香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識嘅外國朋友之中，無一個國家嘅人鍾意/經常講粗口嘅程度係夠香港做。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讀書留學時期識好多外國人同學，出黎做野有時都會接觸外國人。<br />\n<br />\n中日韓台、蒙古、秦國、尼泊爾、<br />\n馬來西亞、非洲黑人、英、美、澳洲等地嘅朋友都識<br />\n<br />\n同佢地傾計，接觸佢地嘅時候，同埋每次傾呢個話題個陣都發覺佢地唔係真係咁常，咁鍾意講粗口。<br />\n<br />\n大家嘅經驗係 ... ? <br />\n<br />\n利申：唔講野會死，講野一定有粗口。"},{"pid":"06dc87f386c5e04fd1c381f85fc978ba53b5d4f7","tid":559710,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80a9e65875474decfcdf042cd2263e31951430ed","tid":559710,"uid":155084,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"06dc87f386c5e04fd1c381f85fc978ba53b5d4f7","tid":559710,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:57:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/200532_4c17fdd29b4d647d248f164ace73753c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F200532_4c17fdd29b4d647d248f164ace73753c.jpeg&h=704ea0f6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}